Alternative styles (LOW)
========================
See:
	http://bootswatch.com/

FontAwesome (LOW)
=================
A font library that fits within Bootstrap's iconic assets.
It provides more icons both in font and in vectorial.
See:
	http://fortawesome.github.com/Font-Awesome/#roadmap



Markdown (VERY-LOW)
===================
Integrate Markdown syntax in order to support a rich text-based syntax to provided formatted contents
See:
	http://daringfireball.net/projects/markdown/
	https://github.com/evilstreak/markdown-js
	http://softwaremaniacs.org/playground/showdown-highlight/
	http://code.google.com/p/pagedown/